init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: she meets a man who seems different from the rest.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was a little sad that she would never see them again, but she was also excited about the prospect of a new relationship.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They dated for a while, and she began to feel like she was falling in love.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She told him about the guys she had dated, and how she had felt an intense connection to them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When she was finished, she looked up at him.
